    "But so much the more went there a fame abroad of him: and great multitudes came together to hear, and to be healed by him of their infirmities.",
    "And he withdrew himself into the wilderness, and prayed.",
    "And it came to pass on a certain day, as he was teaching, that there were Pharisees and doctors of the law sitting by, which were come out of every town of <span class=\"place\">Galilee</span>, and <span class=\"place\">Judæa</span>, and <span class=\"place\">Jerusalem</span>: and the power of the Lord was present to heal them.",
    "And, behold, men brought in a bed a man which was taken with a palsy: and they sought means to bring him in, and to lay him before him.",
