    "Then <span class=\"person\">Jesus</span> answering said unto them, <span class=\"word\">Go your way, and tell <span class=\"person\">John</span> what things ye have seen and heard; how that the blind see, the lame walk, the lepers are cleansed, the deaf hear, the dead are raised, to the poor the gospel is preached.</span>",
